    "Therefore, we capture the textual similarity again in the token space via Equation 3 and the latent space via Equation 2.",
    "C. BaselinesSince there is not much work on contrast sets, we have a limited set of baselines here.",
    "We use the original expert-created contrast sets for the IMDB dataset from the original work [8].",
    "This consists of 488 original test data samples, and 488 contrast samples created by the dataset experts.",
    "Furthermore, we use Polyjuice-generated counterfactuals [5] as contrast sets for comparison."
